{"tha-ap350:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap350:0.2":"Ekapadumiyavagga ","tha-ap350:0.3":"Tinamutthidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap350:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap350:1.2":"lambako nama pabbato; ","tha-ap350:1.3":"Upatisso nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap350:1.4":"abbhokasamhi cankami. ","tha-ap350:2.1":"Migaluddo tada asim, ","tha-ap350:2.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap350:2.3":"Disvana tam devadevam, ","tha-ap350:2.4":"sayambhum aparajitam. ","tha-ap350:3.1":"Vippasannena cittena, ","tha-ap350:3.2":"tada tassa mahesino; ","tha-ap350:3.3":"Nisidanattham buddhassa, ","tha-ap350:3.4":"tinamutthimadasaham. ","tha-ap350:4.1":"Datvana devadevassa, ","tha-ap350:4.2":"bhiyyo cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap350:4.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap350:4.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap350:5.1":"Aciram gatamattam mam, ","tha-ap350:5.2":"migaraja apothayi; ","tha-ap350:5.3":"Sihena pothito santo, ","tha-ap350:5.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap350:6.1":"Asanne me katam kammam, ","tha-ap350:6.2":"buddhasetthe anasave; ","tha-ap350:6.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap350:6.4":"devalokam aganchaham. ","tha-ap350:7.1":"Yupo tattha subho asi, ","tha-ap350:7.2":"punnakammabhinimmito; ","tha-ap350:7.3":"Sahassakando satabhendu, ","tha-ap350:7.4":"dhajalu haritamayo. ","tha-ap350:8.1":"Pabha niddhavate tassa, ","tha-ap350:8.2":"sataramsiva uggato; ","tha-ap350:8.3":"Akinno devakannahi, ","tha-ap350:8.4":"amodim kamakamaham. ","tha-ap350:9.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap350:9.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap350:9.3":"Agantvana manussattam, ","tha-ap350:9.4":"pattomhi asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap350:10.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap350:10.2":"nisidanamadasaham; ","tha-ap350:10.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap350:10.4":"tinamutthiyidam phalam. ","tha-ap350:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap350:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap350:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap350:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinamutthidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap350:13.1":"Tinamutthidayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}